  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201404/bb313e1d3839461b83e057db0bfb808a.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t&quot;Sherlock&quot; fans, Martin Freeman may have just made your day, and maybe even your year.《神探夏洛克》的粉丝们，华生的扮演者<span class=\"web-item\"><span class=\"web-item\">马丁&middot;费里曼的这番话可能会让你今天很高兴，也可能会是你带来一年的好心情。</span></span></p>\n<p>\n\tCo-creators Steven Moffat and Mark Gatiss announced back in February that Season 4 of &quot;Sherlock&quot; may be delayed for two years due to Benedict Cumberbatch and Martin Freeman's busy schedules. However, Freeman teased a bit of secret news that may change things.《神探夏洛克》联合制作人史蒂芬&middot;莫法特和马克&middot;加蒂斯早在二月就表示《神探夏洛克》第四季可能会推迟两年之久，因为两位主演&ldquo;卷福&rdquo;本尼迪克特&middot;康伯巴奇和&ldquo;花生&rdquo; 马丁&middot;弗瑞曼日程都排得很满。不过弗瑞曼日前透露的一点秘密消息，可能会改变一些事情。</p>\n<p>\n\tWhile appearing on Alan Carr's Channel 4 talk show &quot;Chatty Man,&quot; which airs on Friday, April 25, Martin said, &quot;Mark Gatiss may beat me up, but there is an idea for this one-off special that&rsquo;s such a good idea.&quot; Wait, what was that Freeman?!4月25日马丁&middot;弗瑞曼做客英国第四台脱口秀节目《阿兰卡尔谈话秀》时表示，&ldquo;马克&middot;加蒂斯可能会揍我，但我们现在有个想法是，制作一集特别集很不错。&rdquo; 等等，花生这是真的吗！！</p>\n<p>\n\t&quot;As I was listening to it,&quot; Freeman continued, &quot;I thought &lsquo;we&rsquo;ve just got to do this.' It&rsquo;s a fantastic, really mouth-watering idea. But I really don&rsquo;t know when we are going to get to do it.&quot;他接着说道：&ldquo;当时我在听这个提案时，我是觉得我们应该做这个的。这个想法很精彩，也很让人<span class=\"web-item\">垂涎，不过我真的不知道我们会在什么时候制作这个特别集。&rdquo;&nbsp; </span></p>\n<p>\n\t&quot;Mouth-watering,&quot; huh? We trust Watson on that and really hope this one-off episode thing happens soon.&ldquo;让人<span class=\"web-item\">垂涎&rdquo; </span>哈！我们相信华生，也真的很希望特别集能很快制作出来。</p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p605876/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p605876\"><img src=\"